comment: Favors (UTA) makes contact with the ball, causing Hill (LAL) to lose control of it on the drive to the basket.
Johnson (LAL) does not establish legal guarding position and makes leg-to-leg contact with Hayward (UTA) at the start of his drive.
Hill (LAL) sets the off ball screen on Millsap (UTA) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Johnson (LAL) makes contact with Millsap (UTA) going for the steal and the contact forces him OOB.
L-Slash shows Gobert (UTA) comes over Black's (LAL) back and dislodges him while trying to tip the loose ball.
Brown (LAL) commits a take foul on Hayward (UTA).
Clarkson (LAL) commits a take foul on Burke (UTA).
